    <item>
      <title>哈佛大学在众议院调查中猛烈抨击反犹太主义“不作为”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/harvard-slammed-in-house-probe-for-inaction-on-antisemitism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后，国会委员会批评哈佛大学在应对校园反犹太主义方面存在“重大缺陷”，称该校的失败导致了对犹太学生的敌对环境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/harvard-slammed-in-house-probe-for-inaction-on-antisemitism</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:29:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乍得最高法院维持选举结果，对反对派构成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/chad-s-top-court-upholds-election-result-in-blow-to-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍得最高法院驳回了反对派取消 5 月 6 日总统选举的上诉，并宣布该国军事统治者获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/chad-s-top-court-upholds-election-result-in-blow-to-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:28:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究称，特鲁多的住房推动计划受到生产力疲软的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/trudeau-housing-push-challenged-by-weak-productivity-study-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据加拿大住房机构称，加拿大拥有每年建造 70% 以上房屋所需的工人，而市政繁文缛节是建设的主要障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/trudeau-housing-push-challenged-by-weak-productivity-study-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:19:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织表示，美国的开放贸易比中国的关税“服务更好”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/us-better-served-with-open-trade-than-china-tariffs-imf-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织批评拜登政府本周大幅提高部分中国商品关税的决定，强调其警告称世界两大经济体之间的紧张关系可能会损害全球贸易和增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/us-better-served-with-open-trade-than-china-tariffs-imf-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 15:56:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼完成码头将为加沙地带带来新的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/pentagon-finishes-pier-that-will-bring-fresh-aid-to-gaza-strip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼表示，美国已经完成了一座浮动码头的建设，这将有助于为加沙地带提供更多援助，尽管官员们承认新结构无法填补哈马斯和以色列之间战争造成的需求缺口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/pentagon-finishes-pier-that-will-bring-fresh-aid-to-gaza-strip</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 15:27:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯提供与特朗普竞选搭档摊牌的辩论日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/harris-offers-debate-dates-for-showdown-with-trump-running-mate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的竞选团队表示，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯愿意在 7 月 23 日或 8 月 13 日就共和党人唐纳德·特朗普选择的竞选伙伴进行辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/harris-offers-debate-dates-for-showdown-with-trump-running-mate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 14:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科索沃在塞族自治方面做出让步以寻求承认</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/kosovo-offers-concession-on-serb-autonomy-in-bid-for-recognition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科索沃政府在塞尔维亚少数民族自治的关键问题上做出了让步，因为这个巴尔干国家寻求让其加入欧洲委员会的努力重回正轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/kosovo-offers-concession-on-serb-autonomy-in-bid-for-recognition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 14:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布雷纳德称需要征收关税以避免美国出现“中国冲击”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/brainard-says-tariffs-needed-to-avoid-new-china-shock-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的最高经济顾问周四对对中国进口产品征收新关税进行了强有力的辩护，称这些关税对于避免不公平贸易做法造成的经济动荡是必要的，这些做法可能会破坏最近的制造业和就业增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/brainard-says-tariffs-needed-to-avoid-new-china-shock-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登阻止发布机密文件上的采访录音</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/biden-refuses-to-give-house-tapes-of-hur-interview-on-documents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登对他处理机密文件的调查录音行使了行政特权，这加剧了与国会共和党人的争斗，因为他们计划周四投票判定司法部长梅里克·加兰藐视国会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/biden-refuses-to-give-house-tapes-of-hur-interview-on-documents</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 12:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
